<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Isu, ka puma thien ka nuom hi,
 Ka lunggila cheng zing dingin ka hun deih;
 Milim cheng hihsien la, melma nawhmang in,
 Tun nei silin chun vuk sangin vam zawng ka.

[V2]
 Vuk sangin, vamzawng ka, vuk sangin,
 Tun nei silin, chun vuk sangin vam zawng ka.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa Isu gitloh cheng lamang vekin,
 Na thisan lun chun ka gitloh silthieng in;
 Zie thienna chu thildang cheng sangin ka deih,
 Tun nei silin, chun vuk sangin vam zawng ka.

[V4]
 3. Lal Isu van chutphah apat ei enin,
 Ka puma kipie dingin ei panpih in;
 Ka pumin kipieng ka, ka hetna cheng le,
 Tun nei silin, chun vuk sangin vam zawng ka.

[V5]
 4. Lal Isu, kingainiem in zie hi ka ngen,
 Lal deih um, Na keng liem bulah ka ngak hi;
 Thienna ding, Na thisan luong ginnan ka mui,
 Tun nei silin, chun vuk sangin vam zawng ka.

[V6]
 5. Lal Isu, gunchuh taka ka ngak na hei,
 Hung inla, keimah ah lunggil thak siem in;
 Nangmah hun hawlte kuomah Na niel ngei puoi,
 Tun nei silin, chun vuk sangin vam zawng ka.</lyrics>
<title>WHITER THAN SNOW</title>
<hymn_number>191</hymn_number>
</song>